  28 May 2010; Joseph Jezak <josejx@gentoo.org> cucumber-0.7.2.ebuild,
  cucumber-0.7.3.ebuild:
  Marked ~ppc/~ppc64 for bug #318949.

  24 May 2010; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> cucumber-0.7.2.ebuild,
  cucumber-0.7.3.ebuild:
  Add ~sparc/~x86 wrt #318949

*cucumber-0.7.3 (20 May 2010)

  20 May 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.7.3.ebuild:
  Version bump. Minor new features.

*cucumber-0.7.2 (08 May 2010)

  08 May 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.7.2.ebuild:
  Version bump. Now uses Gherkin for feature parsing. Dropped ppc, sparc,
  x86 due to new dependencies: bug 318949.

  31 Mar 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -cucumber-0.6.1.ebuild,
  -cucumber-0.6.2.ebuild:
  Remove old versions.

*cucumber-0.6.4 (31 Mar 2010)

  31 Mar 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.6.4.ebuild:
  Version bump. Bug fixes and minor new features.

*cucumber-0.6.3 (03 Mar 2010)

  03 Mar 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.6.3.ebuild:
  Version bump with minor bug fixes and new features. Also enable cucumber
  tests.

  03 Mar 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -cucumber-0.4.0.ebuild:
  Remove old version.

  13 Feb 2010; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> cucumber-0.4.0.ebuild,
  cucumber-0.5.3.ebuild, cucumber-0.6.1.ebuild, cucumber-0.6.2.ebuild:
  Add ~sparc

*cucumber-0.6.2 (20 Jan 2010)

  20 Jan 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.6.2.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  14 Jan 2010; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> cucumber-0.6.1.ebuild:
  Marking cucumber-0.6.1 ~ppc for bug 300739

