  reporting in bug #300739.

*cucumber-0.6.1 (03 Jan 2010)

  03 Jan 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.6.1.ebuild:
  Version bump. Tag handling has changed in an incompatible way.

  03 Jan 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -cucumber-0.5.1.ebuild,
