*cucumber-0.5.2 (22 Dec 2009)

  22 Dec 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.5.2.ebuild:
  Version bump with new features to support cuke4duke and jruby.

*cucumber-0.5.1-r1 (18 Dec 2009)

  18 Dec 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.5.1-r1.ebuild:
  Install cucumber binary.

*cucumber-0.5.1 (18 Dec 2009)

  18 Dec 2009; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +cucumber-0.5.1.ebuild:
  Version bump. Rails support has been split off to cucumber-rails.
  Converted to use ruby-fakegem.

